Package: validate.log
Maintainer: Mark van der Loo <mark.vanderloo@gmail.com>
License: GPL-3
Title: Logging framework for data cleaning
LazyData: no
Type: Package
LazyLoad: yes
Authors@R: c(person("Mark", "van der Loo",role=c("cre","aut"),email="mark.vanderloo@gmail.com")
    , person("Edwin", "de Jonge", role="aut") )
Description: A logging framework that can keep track of every change performed
    on a data set. Functions that are aware of the framework can be registerd for
    logging using either a built-in logger or one that is custom-built.
Version: 0.0.1
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
URL: https://github.com/data-cleaning/validate
BugReports: https://github.com/data-cleaning/validate.log/issues
Date: 2015-08-28
Imports: methods, RSQLite
Suggests: testthat, knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
